---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="FOIA Request Letter Template — LoopholeDB"
  description="Free fill-in-the-blank Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) request letter template. Print or save as PDF."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>
    <div class="template-toolbar no-print">
      <div class="toolbar-inner">
        <a href="/us/dealing-with-government/foia-requests" class="toolbar-back">← FOIA Requests</a>
        <div class="toolbar-actions">
          <p class="toolbar-hint">Fill in the <mark>[BRACKETED FIELDS]</mark>, then print or save as PDF.</p>
          <button onclick="window.print()" class="btn btn--primary">Print / Save as PDF</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-wrap">
      <article class="document">

        <div class="doc-sender">
          <p>[YOUR FULL NAME]</p>
          <p>[YOUR STREET ADDRESS]</p>
          <p>[CITY, STATE, ZIP CODE]</p>
          <p>[YOUR PHONE NUMBER]</p>
          <p>[YOUR EMAIL ADDRESS]</p>
        </div>

        <p class="doc-date">[DATE]</p>

        <div class="doc-recipient">
          <p>FOIA Officer</p>
          <p>[AGENCY NAME]</p>
          <p>[AGENCY MAILING ADDRESS OR FOIA PORTAL URL]</p>
          <p>[CITY, STATE, ZIP CODE]</p>
        </div>

        <p class="doc-re"><strong>Re: Freedom of Information Act Request</strong></p>

        <p>Dear FOIA Officer:</p>

        <p>
          Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, 5 U.S.C. § 552, I hereby request access to and copies of the following agency records:
        </p>

        <div class="doc-box">
          <p>
            [DESCRIBE THE RECORDS YOU ARE REQUESTING. Be as specific as possible: include relevant dates, names, locations, subject matter, document types, or any other details that will help the agency locate the records. Example: "All inspection reports, correspondence, and internal memoranda relating to [FACILITY NAME / ADDRESS] from [START DATE] through [END DATE]."]
          </p>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Fee Category</strong></p>
        <p>To help determine my fee category, I am (check one):</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>☐ A representative of the news media. My intended use is: [DESCRIBE JOURNALISTIC PURPOSE]</li>
          <li>☐ An educational institution or noncommercial scientific institution</li>
          <li>☐ A commercial requester</li>
          <li>☐ A member of the general public</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Fee Waiver Request</strong></p>
        <p>
          I request a fee waiver pursuant to 5 U.S.C. § 552(a)(4)(A)(iii) on the grounds that disclosure of the requested information is in the public interest because it is likely to contribute significantly to public understanding of the operations or activities of the government, and disclosure is not primarily in my commercial interest. Specifically: [EXPLAIN WHY RELEASE WOULD BENEFIT THE PUBLIC].
        </p>
        <p>
          Alternatively, if a full fee waiver is not granted, please notify me before incurring costs exceeding $[AMOUNT, e.g., $25.00].
        </p>

        <p><strong>Format of Response</strong></p>
        <p>
          I prefer to receive responsive records in electronic format (PDF or searchable text) sent to the email address above. If records are only available in paper format, please provide copies.
        </p>

        <p><strong>Withholding and Exemptions</strong></p>
        <p>
          If any portion of the requested records is withheld, I request that you provide a Vaughn index identifying each withheld document and specifying the exemption(s) relied upon and the reasons the exemption applies. Please release any reasonably segregable, non-exempt portions of withheld records.
        </p>

        <p><strong>Expedited Processing</strong> (complete only if applicable)</p>
        <p>
          I request expedited processing pursuant to 5 U.S.C. § 552(a)(6)(E) because [COMPELLING NEED — e.g., "there is an imminent threat to life or physical safety" or "I am a journalist and there is urgency to inform the public about actual or alleged government activity"]. I certify that this statement is true and correct to the best of my knowledge.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have any questions or need clarification about this request, please contact me at the phone number or email address listed above. I look forward to your response within the 20 business days required by 5 U.S.C. § 552(a)(6)(A).
        </p>

        <p>Sincerely,</p>

        <div class="doc-sig">
          <div class="sig-line"></div>
          <p>[YOUR PRINTED NAME]</p>
        </div>

        <div class="doc-footer-note no-print">
          <p><strong>Tips:</strong> Send to the agency's official FOIA portal at <a href="https://www.foia.gov" target="_blank">foia.gov</a> or by certified mail. Keep your tracking number. If you don't receive a response within 20 business days, you may file an administrative appeal citing a "constructive denial." State agencies have their own open records laws — search "[STATE] public records request" for the correct form and recipient.</p>
        </div>

      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  <div class="no-print"><Footer /></div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .template-toolbar {
    background: var(--color-espresso);
    padding: 0.85rem 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
  }
  .toolbar-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .toolbar-back {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(242,235,224,0.6);
    transition: color var(--transition);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .toolbar-back:hover { color: var(--color-cream); }
  .toolbar-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .toolbar-hint {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgba(242,235,224,0.55);
  }
  .toolbar-hint mark {
    background: rgba(242,235,224,0.15);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.1em 0.3em;
  }

  .doc-wrap {
    background: var(--color-cream-dark);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  .document {
    background: #fff;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: 3.5rem 4rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #111;
  }

  .document p { margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }

  .doc-sender { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .doc-sender p { margin: 0; line-height: 1.55; }

  .doc-date { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .doc-recipient { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
  .doc-recipient p { margin: 0; line-height: 1.55; }

  .doc-re { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

  .document ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }
  .document ul li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }

  .checklist { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  .checklist li { padding-left: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .doc-box {
    border: 1px solid #bbb;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: #fafafa;
    min-height: 120px;
  }
  .doc-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-style: italic; }

  .doc-sig {
    margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .sig-line {
    width: 260px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #888;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .doc-footer-note {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: #f5f0e8;
    border-left: 3px solid #b08860;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #555;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }
  .doc-footer-note p { margin: 0; }
  .doc-footer-note a { color: #4B3520; }

  @media print {
    .no-print { display: none !important; }
    .doc-wrap { background: #fff; padding: 0; }
    .document { box-shadow: none; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 100%; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .document { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .toolbar-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>
